{"id":89733,"title":"Bone. Maximizing bone health--magnesium, BMD and fractures.","abstract":"The contribution of nutrition to bone health has been heavily debated for many years resulting in unclear recommendations for patients regarding prevention of bone loss and subsequent fractures. A recent cohort study has examined the relationships between magnesium intake, BMD and fractures.","date":"2014-04-21","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24686202","annotations":[{"name":"Osteoporosis","weight":0.759865,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Osteoporosis"},{"name":"Nutrition","weight":0.719721,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nutrition"},{"name":"Cohort study","weight":0.567794,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cohort_study"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.553926,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Bone","weight":0.508819,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bone"},{"name":"Bone density","weight":0.291989,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bone_density"},{"name":"Preventive medicine","weight":0.211485,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preventive_medicine"},{"name":"Magnesium","weight":0.113889,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magnesium"},{"name":"Bone fracture","weight":0.0650786,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bone_fracture"},{"name":"Cohort (statistics)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cohort_(statistics)"},{"name":"Intake","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intake"},{"name":"Maximization (ethics)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maximization_(ethics)"}]}
